name: YYLLOC_DEFAULT
value:
do \
    { \
        if ((n) > 0) \
            current = (rhs)[1]; \
        else \
            current = -1; \
    } while (0)

name: YY_IGNORE_MAYBE_UNINITIALIZED_BEGIN
value:
_Pragma ("GCC diagnostic push")                                     \
    _Pragma ("GCC diagnostic ignored \"-Wuninitialized\"")              \
    _Pragma ("GCC diagnostic ignored \"-Wmaybe-uninitialized\"")

name: YYSTACK_RELOCATE
value:
do                                                                  \
      {                                                                 \
        YYPTRDIFF_T yynewbytes;                                         \
        YYCOPY (&yyptr->Stack_alloc, Stack, yysize);                    \
        Stack = &yyptr->Stack_alloc;                                    \
        yynewbytes = yystacksize * YYSIZEOF (*Stack) + YYSTACK_GAP_MAXIMUM; \
        yyptr += yynewbytes / YYSIZEOF (*yyptr);                        \
      }                                                                 \
    while (0)

name: YYCOPY
value:
do                                        \
        {                                       \
          YYPTRDIFF_T yyi;                      \
          for (yyi = 0; yyi < (Count); yyi++)   \
            (Dst)[yyi] = (Src)[yyi];            \
        }                                       \
      while (0)

name: YYBACKUP
value:
do                                                              \
    if (yychar == YYEMPTY)                                        \
      {                                                           \
        yychar = (Token);                                         \
        yylval = (Value);                                         \
        YYPOPSTACK (yylen);                                       \
        yystate = *yyssp;                                         \
        goto yybackup;                                            \
      }                                                           \
    else                                                          \
      {                                                           \
        yyerror (&yylloc, scanner, extra, YY_("syntax error: cannot back up")); \
        YYERROR;                                                  \
      }                                                           \
  while (0)

name: YYLLOC_DEFAULT
value:
do                                                                  \
      if (N)                                                            \
        {                                                               \
          (Current).first_line   = YYRHSLOC (Rhs, 1).first_line;        \
          (Current).first_column = YYRHSLOC (Rhs, 1).first_column;      \
          (Current).last_line    = YYRHSLOC (Rhs, N).last_line;         \
          (Current).last_column  = YYRHSLOC (Rhs, N).last_column;       \
        }                                                               \
      else                                                              \
        {                                                               \
          (Current).first_line   = (Current).last_line   =              \
            YYRHSLOC (Rhs, 0).last_line;                                \
          (Current).first_column = (Current).last_column =              \
            YYRHSLOC (Rhs, 0).last_column;                              \
        }                                                               \
    while (0)

name: YY_SYMBOL_PRINT
value:
do {                                                                      \
  if (yydebug)                                                            \
    {                                                                     \
      YYFPRINTF (stderr, "%s ", Title);                                   \
      yy_symbol_print (stderr,                                            \
                  Kind, Value, Location, scanner, extra); \
      YYFPRINTF (stderr, "\n");                                           \
    }                                                                     \
} while (0)

name: YY_REDUCE_PRINT
value:
do {                                    \
  if (yydebug)                          \
    yy_reduce_print (yyssp, yyvsp, yylsp, Rule, scanner, extra); \
} while (0)
